### 获取网站可登录信息
GET {{host}}/v1/website_login_context/get_webside_infos
Authorization: {{token}}

### 创建网页登录上下文
POST {{host}}/v1/website_login_context
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

{
  "platform": "xiao_hong_shu",
  "purpose": "blog",
  "browser_context": "{}",
  "status": 1
}

### 更新网页登录上下文
PUT {{host}}/v1/website_login_context/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

{
  "browser_context": "{\"name\": 1}",
  "tags": ["1" , "2"]
}

### 分页查询
GET {{host}}/v1/website_login_context?page=1&page_size=10&platform=&purpose=&tag=
Authorization: {{token}}

### 删除
DELETE {{host}}/v1/website_login_context/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

### 获取详情
GET {{host}}/v1/website_login_context/8
Authorization: {{token}}
